hitcounters2-rest-incrementnottrue: Resturned by the REST API when the 'increment' parameter in the body of the POST data is not true
hitcounters2-rest-pagedoesnotexist: Returned by the REST API when attempting to increment the hit counter of a page that does not exist
hitcounters2-rest-pageidzero: Returned by the REST API when attempting to increment the hit counter for a page with id zero
